<li><a href="https://github.com/komatits/specfem2d" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SPECFEM2D - Spectral element seismic modelling code in 2D Cartesian Coordinates</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/komatits/specfem3d" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SPECFEM3D - Spectral element seismic modelling code in 3D Cartesian Coordinates</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/komatits/specfem3d_globe" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SPECFEM3D_GLOBE - Spectral element seismic modelling code in 3D Spherical Coordinates</a></li>
</ul>
<h4 id="有限差分"><a href="#有限差分" class="headerlink" title="有限差分"></a>有限差分</h4><ul>
